This directory contains Version 2.5 of SB-Prolog.  This version
currently runs on machines like Vax, Sun-3, HP-9000, Amiga, etc.
It will not run on alignment restricted processors like the Sun-4,
Pyramid-98x and SGI Iris.  A version that does run on such
alignment-restricted systems is in the directory ../v3.0, but
that version currently lacks some builtin predicates (clause/{2,3},
listing/{0,1}, recorda/recordz/recorded).

Benchmarking: There are a couple of benchmarks in the
directory bench, see bench/README.

Some porting information can be found in sbp_ports/
---
